      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hidden md:block">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">

        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <a href="/zh/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">

            <div class="relative h-14 w-auto flex items-center justify-center">

              <svg height="46" viewBox="0 0 85 55" fill="currentColor" class="text-white group-hover:text-laser transition-colors duration-300">
                <path d="M0 0 H13 V40 H0 V0 Z" />
                <path d="M14 40 H26 L26 20 Z" />
                <path d="M30 40 L45 40 L37 13 Z" />
                <path d="M38.5 8 L48 40 L61 40 L49 0 H40.5 Z" />
                <path d="M54.5 8 L64 40 L77 40 L65 0 H56.5 Z" />
                <text x="73" y="8" font-family="Arial" font-size="10" fill="currentColor">®</text>
                <text x="15.5" y="52" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-weight="bold" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor">Precision</text>
                <text x="59" y="52" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-weight="bold" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" fill="currentColor">Engraving</text>
              </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center h-10">
              <span class="font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider text-white group-hover:text-laser transition-colors duration-300">L M PRECISION</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] text-steel-500 uppercase">Pte Ltd</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <p class="font-body text-steel-400 max-w-md mb-6">
            5轴激光雕刻、3D 模具曲面加工及精密电极制造专家。为医疗、航空航天及注塑行业提供高保真组件标识与纹理解决方案。
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-precision-green rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-precision-green">承接新项目</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-steel-400 uppercase mb-6">服务项目</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><a href="/zh/#services" class="font-body text-steel-300 hover:text-laser transition-colors text-sm">3D 模具雕刻</a></li>
            <li><a href="/zh/#services" class="font-body text-steel-300 hover:text-laser transition-colors text-sm">5轴激光加工</a></li>
            <li><a href="/zh/#services" class="font-body text-steel-300 hover:text-laser transition-colors text-sm">电极制造</a></li>
            <li><a href="/zh/#services" class="font-body text-steel-300 hover:text-laser transition-colors text-sm">型腔 ID 雕刻</a></li>
            <li><a href="/zh/#services" class="font-body text-steel-300 hover:text-laser transition-colors text-sm">表面纹理加工</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-steel-400 uppercase mb-6">核心能力</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li><span class="font-body text-steel-300 text-sm">复杂模具表面</span></li>
            <li><span class="font-body text-steel-300 text-sm">无倒扣死角 (5轴)</span></li>
            <li><span class="font-body text-steel-300 text-sm">石墨与铜电极</span></li>
            <li><span class="font-body text-steel-300 text-sm">Logo 与版本打标</span></li>
            <li><span class="font-body text-steel-300 text-sm">注塑模具支持</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-steel-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-steel-500">
          © {currentYear} L M Precision Pte Ltd. 版权所有。新加坡。
        </p>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <a href="/zh/privacy" class="font-mono text-xs text-steel-500 hover:text-laser transition-colors">
            隐私政策
          </a>
          <span class="text-steel-700">|</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-steel-600">
            UEN: <span class="text-steel-400 tracking-wider">{uenNumber}</span>
          </span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>